586
00:29:42,759 --> 00:29:45,167
J'espère que Joel pensera pareil.

587
00:29:45,292 --> 00:29:48,300
- Tu l'as vu ?
- Non, mais voilà ton copain.

588
00:29:50,386 --> 00:29:52,230
- Salut.
